This paper primarily focuses on data security in databases, which falls under the category of cs.DB (Database). It also discusses techniques for fortifying and strengthening databases, which can be categorized under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). Additionally, the paper mentions the importance of privacy and integrity of data, which can be related to cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
